hara":[{"id":200101,"motion":100}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So it's worth the effort, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I would like you to get fully trained@and ready..."},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...before Walpurgisnacht gets here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200301,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Walpurgisnacht...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yes."},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I was only told about it recently, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]An extremely dangerous Witch is expected@to appear in this town in the near future."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":201}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, defeating Walpurgisnacht@with our combined strength..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's our current goal."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Miss Akemi."},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]According to Kyubey, you also have@the potential to become a Magical Girl."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200301,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]M-Me...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200501}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMam